title: The Top 23 Most Beautiful American Campsites
text:
Photo: Ethan Fitchner 
This site comes with expansive views over Arizona's Coconino National Forest. There is plenty of space to explore during the day and unbelievable stars at night. Learn more. Please remember to follow local regulations regarding campsite use and practice Leave No Trace ethics on all of your adventures.
